---
---
<header class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="hero-sub animate-fade-in">Welcome to my portfolio</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title animate-fade-in-up">HIROTO'S WORKSPACE</h1> <p class="hero-desc animate-fade-in-up-delayed">Web制作、デザイン、日々のクリエイティブをまとめた場所です。</p> <a href="#about" class="btn animate-fade-in-up-delayed2">Discover More</a>
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  .hero {
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 90% 10%, #eff6ff 0%, #ffffff 60%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    background-color: var(--color-dark);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.15);
  }
  .btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25);
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }
  .animate-fade-in { animation: fadeIn 1s forwards; }
  .animate-fade-in-up { animation: fadeInUp 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards; }
  .animate-fade-in-up-delayed { animation: fadeInUp 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .animate-fade-in-up-delayed2 { animation: fadeInUp 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.4s forwards; opacity: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  }
</style>